@section Main options

@table @option
@item -L
Show license.

@item -h
Show help.

@item -formats
Show available formats, codecs, protocols, ...

@item -f fmt
Force format.

@item -i filename
input filename

@item -y
Overwrite output files.

@item -t duration
Set the recording time in seconds.
@code{hh:mm:ss[.xxx]} syntax is also supported.

