Seek to given time position in seconds.
@code{hh:mm:ss[.xxx]} syntax is also supported.

@item -title string
Set the title.

@item -author string
Set the author.

@item -copyright string
Set the copyright.

@item -comment string
Set the comment.

@item -target type
Specify target file type ("vcd", "svcd", "dvd", "dv", "pal-vcd",
